TIMING-4#1 Critical Warning
Invalid primary clock redefinition on a clock tree  
Invalid clock redefinition on a clock tree. The primary clock u_clk_wiz/inst/clk_in1 is defined downstream of clock sys_clk_100mhz and overrides its insertion delay and/or waveform definition
