TIMING-6#1 Critical Warning
No common primary clock between related clocks  
The clocks cam_pclk and clk_out1_clk_wiz_0 are related (timed together) but they have no common primary clock. The design could fail in hardware. To find a timing path between these clocks, run the following command: report_timing -from [get_clocks cam_pclk] -to [get_clocks clk_out1_clk_wiz_0]
Related violations: <none>

